      \u043C\u0438\u0442\u044C!\tZampe in alto! Il gatto ha bisogno di un secondo!\r\nui_chooseaccount_content\t\"Choose
      the account you want to continue.\r\nOnce you choose, another one will be deleted
      permanently.\"\t\"Ch\u1ECDn t\xE0i kho\u1EA3n b\u1EA1n mu\u1ED1n ti\u1EBFp
      t\u1EE5c. \nSau khi ch\u1ECDn, t\xE0i kho\u1EA3n c\xF2n l\u1EA1i s\u1EBD b\u1ECB
      x\xF3a v\u0129nh vi\u1EC5n.\"\tEscolha a conta que deseja continuar. Ao escolher,
      a outra ser\xE1 exclu\xEDda permanentemente.\tDevam etmek istedi\u011Finiz
      hesab\u0131 se\xE7in. Se\xE7tikten sonra di\u011Fer hesap kal\u0131c\u0131
      olarak silinecek.\tW\xE4hle das Konto, mit dem du fortfahren m\xF6chtest. Das
      andere wird dauerhaft gel\xF6scht.\tChoisissez le compte avec lequel vous voulez
      continuer. L'autre sera supprim\xE9 d\xE9finitivement.\tPilih akun yang ingin
      Anda lanjutkan. Setelah dipilih, akun lain akan dihapus secara permanen.\tElige
      la cuenta con la que deseas continuar. La otra se eliminar\xE1 permanentemente.\t\u0412\u044B\u0431\u0435\u0440\u0438\u0442\u0435
